      <title>中国允许人民币贬值，因资金外流和美元考验中国人民银行的掌控力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/china-weakens-yuan-fix-to-lowest-since-january-to-allow-declines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于资本外流激增和美元坚挺，迫使央行放松管制，中国表示允许人民币兑美元走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-23/china-weakens-yuan-fix-to-lowest-since-january-to-allow-declines</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 23 May 2024 01:19:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于美联储前景鹰派，油价第四个交易日延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在周三收于三个月来的最低水平后扩大跌幅，原因是有迹象表明美联储可能会在更长时间内维持较高的利率，这可能会打压能源需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-23</guid>
